quran[27{c,v,t}:
89,24,kahe ga kash mein ne apni zindagi ( javedani ke liye ) kuch agay bheja hota
89,25,to is din nah koi khuda ke azaab ki terhan ka ( kisi ko ) azaab day ga
89,26,aur nah koi waisa jakarna jakray ga
89,27,ae itminan panay wali rooh !
89,28,apne perwar-digaar ki taraf lout chal. to is se raazi woh tujh se raazi
89,29,to mere ( mumtaz ) bundon mein shaamil ho ja
89,30,aur meri bahisht mein daakhil ho ja
90,1,hamein is shehar ( mecca ) ki qasam
90,2,aur tum isi shehar mein to rehtay ho
90,3,aur baap ( yani aadam ) aur is ki aulaad ki qasam
90,4,ke hum ne ensaan ko takleef ( ki haalat ) mein ( rehne wala ) banaya hai
90,5,kiya woh khayaal rakhta hai ke is par koi qaboo nah paye ga
90,6,kehta hai ke mein ne bohat sa maal barbaadkiya
90,7,kiya usay yeh gumaan hai ke is ko kisi ne dekha nahi
90,8,bhala hum ne is ko do ankhen nahi den ?
90,9,aur zabaan aur do hont ( nahi diye )
90,10,( yeh cheeze bhi den ) aur is ko ( kher o shar ke ) dono raste bhi dikha diye
90,11,magar woh ghaati par se ho kar nah guzra
90,12,aur tumkiya samjhay ke ghaatikiya hai ?
90,13,kisi ( ki ) gardan ka chhurana
90,14,ya bhook ke din khana khilana
90,15,yateem rishta daar ko
90,16,ya faqeer khaakhsaar ko
90,17,phir un logon mein bhi ( daakhil ) ho jo imaan laaye aur sabr ki nasiyaat aur ( logon par ) shafqat karne ki wasiyat karte rahay
90,18,yahi log sahib Saadat hain
90,19,aur jinhon ne hamari ayaton ko nah maana woh badbakht hain
90,20,yeh log aag mein band kar diye jayen ge
